Subject: [PATCH] Input: i8042 - add TUXEDO Stellaris 15 Slim Gen6 AMD to i8042 quirk table
Git-commit: 3870e2850b56306d1d1e435c5a1ccbccd7c59291
Patch-mainline: v6.12-rc1
References: stable-fixes

The Gen6 devices have the same problem and the same Solution as the Gen5
ones.

Some TongFang barebones have touchpad and/or keyboard issues after
suspend, fixable with nomux + reset + noloop + nopnp. Luckily, none of
them have an external PS/2 port so this can safely be set for all of
them.

I'm not entirely sure if every device listed really needs all four quirks,
but after testing and production use, no negative effects could be
observed when setting all four.

